' ========== Connections ==========
DataEngineer --> BQML : Prepare data\nTrain model
DataScientist --> KFP : Create ML pipeline
KFP --> BQML : Orchestrate\nmodel training
KFP --> CloudStorage : Store model artifacts
KFP --> AIPlatform : Deploy model
KFP --> VertexAI : Deploy model
KFP --> Dataflow : Trigger data processing
AIPlatform <--> ScaNNContainer : Serve embeddings\nand similarity matching
VertexAI --> ScaNNContainer : Serve model\nfor real-time inference
BQML --> Dataflow : Transform and process data
Dataflow --> CloudStorage : Export embeddings
ScaNNContainer --> Datastore : Retrieve item metadata
GoogleAdsAPI <- DataScientist : Activate\nlookalike audiences
DataScientist -> DataStudio : Create visualizations
